snippet.title: Beast In Black - Cry Out For A Hero (Cover)
snippet.description:
I wanted to be a vocalist that no one could imitate, and of course other singers my age couldn't easily get my attention. Yes, but Yannis, he was a little different. At a young age he was already at the top and his live performances were amazing. I take my hat’s off to him!

When my friend Leo first recommended Beast In Black for the next cover song, I was a little questioned if I could sing this song well enough. The instrumental music and mixing were almost complete, but due to my unstable finances and poor physical condition, I had to admit that I couldn't sing this song right now. In the end, Patrick's Godlike Solo and Leo's solid mix hasn't been released for nearly seven months. But they waited for me without any complaints.

For a long time, I focused on resetting my life and recovering my body. Eventually I came back, and this song is the fruit of my efforts. I am now ready to fly again.

Money and health are also essential to music. But above all, we can't do music alone. I am grateful that I still have good friends. Thanks!
Beast In Black - Cry Out For A Hero(Cover)

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals and Video Editing
Patrick Fallang (Symmetric Chaos, Norway) - Lead Guitars, Choirs
Leo Peña (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Rhythm Guitars, Bass Guitars, Drum Programming, Mixing, Mastering and Producing
